<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF37FF515AB6FD5AFC746388" author="Steenis, J. van &amp; Hauser, M. &amp; Zuijlen, M. P. van" box="[680,967,727,753]" pageId="250" pageNumber="251" pagination="145 - 165" refId="ref374819" refString="Steenis, J. van, Hauser, M. &amp; Zuijlen, M. P. van (2017) Revision of the Eumerus barbarus species group (Diptera, Syrphidae) from the western Mediterranean Basin. Bonn Zoological Bulletin, 66 (2), 145 - 165." type="journal article" year="2017">
Steenis 
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF37FF515B1FFD5AFC896388" box="[769,826,727,753]" italics="true" pageId="250" pageNumber="251">et al.</emphasis>
(2017: 149)
</bibRefCitation>
considered the single MZUF male as the 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FF37FF5158D9FD76FE9E626C" box="[199,301,763,789]" pageId="250" pageNumber="251">holotype</typeStatus>
